OL,3,CBereaved mother calls for better
OL,4,Csupport around baby loss
OL,6,FNoah was diagnosed with this condition
OL,7,Fwhen Ellie was 12 weeks into her
OL,8,Fpregnancy. From this moment, through
OL,9,FNoah's death, and now five months on,
OL,10,Fshe said she's been unsupported by the
OL,11,FNHS.
OL,13,FShe said: "They put Noah on to me to
OL,14,Fbegin with and I felt him take his
OL,15,Ffirst and last breath and I felt a
OL,16,Fslight twitch in his leg and that's a
OL,17,Fmemory that forever is going to stay
OL,18,Fwith me - knowing that he decided to
OL,19,Fchose me to pass away on."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/7
