OL,3,CBereaved mother calls for better
OL,4,Csupport around baby loss
OL,6,FShe explained that after Noah's death,
OL,7,Fshe had "begged" for support.
OL,9,FShe said: "We were told there and then
OL,10,Fthat we would have support from
OL,11,Fbereavement nurses specialist care six
OL,12,Fweeks after I had a baby and the only
OL,13,Fthing we have received is a
OL,14,Fbereavement midwife we haven't
OL,15,Freceived any specialist care after
OL,16,Fthat, so where is our support?"
