OL,3,CBereaved mother calls for better
OL,4,Csupport around baby loss
OL,6,FNow Ellie wants to prevent other
OL,7,Fbereaved parents going through similar
OL,8,Fstruggles, and is calling on the NHS
OL,9,Fto step up its support services to
OL,10,Fensure expectant parents facing
OL,11,Fserious diagnosis or infant loss are
OL,12,Fnot left fending for themselves.
OL,14,FShe said: "The NHS need to start
OL,15,Fproviding support, especially
OL,16,Fbereavement support, for grieving
OL,17,Ffamilies especially like mine so we
OL,18,Fcan prevent things like severe mental
OL,19,Fhealth for baby loss like my family
OL,20,Fhas experienced."
