OL,3,CBereaved mother calls for better
OL,4,Csupport around baby loss
OL,6,FThe Lullaby Trust is a charity
OL,7,Fdedicated to keeping babies safe and
OL,8,Fgrieving families supported.
OL,10,FJenny Ward, from the charity, said:
OL,11,F"We know the impact of losing a baby
OL,12,Fis obviously devastating for everybody
OL,13,Finvolved and can go on for quite a
OL,14,Fwhile. We want to make sure people are
OL,15,Foffered support at the first point at
OL,16,Fwhich they need it, and that they know
OL,17,Fthat that is there whenever they go
OL,18,Fback to it.
