OL,3,CBereaved mother calls for better
OL,4,Csupport around baby loss
OL,6,F"There are some waiting lists for
OL,7,Fformal counselling but there are other
OL,8,Fcharities and organisations that can
OL,9,Foffer support."
OL,11,FSince speaking out, Ellie said other
OL,12,Ffamilies have been in touch with her.
OL,14,FShe said: "That's what worries me the
OL,15,Fmost, knowing the NHS won't help not
OL,16,Fjust my family but families that are
OL,17,Fstruggling as well as we are."
